data.description: This Stunning Well Maintained 5 Bed 3 Bath Boasts the Feeling of Home as you Come through the Grand Entryway with Glass French Doors to Dining Room, Hardwood Floor through the Great Room with Gas Fireplace and Custom Mantle, into the Chef's Kitchen with Top-of-the-Line Appliances and Breakfast Area. First Floor Complete with Split Floor Plan. Tons of Space Upstairs plus Bathroom! Complete with Brick Workshop and storage Building outside. Enjoy evenings on Back Covered Porch with Fenced Yard.
